caption: This picture totally describes me! I'm a huge volleyball player, so when I'm on the court, I like to be wild and concentrate, but then I'm able to get dressed in high heels for any special occasion. I've done that before! I've had volleyball practice from 3-5, and then at 7, was the sport awards at my school. And I had to get dressed up in heels and a dress. But anywayssssssss when I play volleyball at practice, I like playing your songs, especially Groove because it gets me going. Like it just changes my whole mood. And to meet you guys again would be insane. I'm not rich or anything, so it's hard to just fly here and there to see you. It would be amazing for me and my friend Perla to meet you. (She's never met you guys) and she's been dying to see you perform and just hang out. It would mean the world to just talk to you. No phones in your face, and a conversation that goes longer than 5 minutes. I love you both endlessly!??? @jackjohnsonofficial @jackgilinskyofficial @jackandjackofficial #jackandjack #jackjohnson #jackgilinksy
